    title: "HIPAA-Compliant Healthcare Advertising: What Every Marketer Must Know",
    excerpt: "Healthcare advertising on Google and Meta can create HIPAA compliance risks if done incorrectly. This guide explains the rules and how to advertise safely and effectively.",
    publishDate: "2025-05-01",
