    title: "How Much Do Google Ads Cost in 2025? Complete Pricing Guide",
    excerpt: "Google Ads costs vary by industry, keyword, and competition. This guide covers everything you need to know about Google Ads pricing in 2025: average CPCs, monthly budgets, management fees, and ROI calculation.",
    publishDate: "2025-06-20",
    author: "Woofer Digital Team",
